DESC="The gopchop utility is an mpeg video editing tool.
The gopchop utility is a video editing tool designed to take
MPEG2-PS files and perform Group-of-Pictures editing
(\"GOP-accurate editing\"). No re-encoding is performed, which
drastically improves editing speed.
